Usage: time_info [-help] [<name>] [-current] [-report] [-stamp]
                 [-table <string>]

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<name>              # Specifies stage name (string, optional)
-current            # Specifies report current stage (bool, optional)
-report             # Specifies report all stages up to this point
                    # (bool, optional)
-stamp              # Specifies create a time stamp (bool, optional)
-table <string>     # Specifies metrics table ID to support multiple tables
                    # (default is 'default') (string, optional)